**HARUG!** is the Harper Adams R User Group

This site is devoted to the R programming, Python, Statistics and Data Science community at Harper Adams University. We meet Wednesdays at 4pm UK time on Teams and via our [Slack workspace anytime](https://join.slack.com/t/ha-eda-party/shared_invite/zt-w19od3dz-6bjo~dTC_GQeSUUv3B8XzQ) (please join with your full real name, e.g. "Florence Nightingale").

![](img/slack.png){width="40"} [Slack workspace: Join us](https://join.slack.com/t/harper-adams-rug/shared_invite/zt-azcm9z6s-WsY9JXvAs8DW1DLQuU3USg) (kindly register with your real name, e.g. "Ronald Fisher")

![](img/youtube.png){width="35"} [Youtube channel](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOEuOH6cY8yisodud25hb7w)

-   Research methods in statistics and AI applications

-   Build data analysis skills and capacity

-   Group problem solving, live coding

-   Tutorials and resource sharing

-   Community

